title: One Nation Under Lee (Singapore Documentary)
description:
One Nation Under Lee

One Nation Under Lee is a documentary about Lee Kuan Yew and how he iron-fistedly subjugated an entire nation in the guise of democracy. The materials in this film are not those you can find in our history textbooks. Feel free to watch, download and distribute.

Title: One Nation Under Lee
Genre: Documentary
Runtime: 45 min.
Language: English
Director: Seelan Palay
Country: Singapore
